    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >语言设置：</h2>你可以通过如下操作将游戏语言设置为简体中文：点击游戏菜单中的“Settings”选项<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏内容：</h2>即时战斗，深度策略。游戏这两个元素融合融合在了一起，既要关注战场，又要思考策略。<br>打造出独一无二的牌组、遇见无数离奇的怪物、发现威力强大的宝藏、还能和世界上其他玩家对战！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><br>玩家的对战：当你完成尖塔后，你可以和世界上其他玩家进行排名对战。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063140/extras/3db78539540fbe205e21c4f94aaec6a7.poster.avif?t=1569203209\" width=536 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063140/extras/3db78539540fbe205e21c4f94aaec6a7.webm?t=1569203209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063140/extras/3db78539540fbe205e21c4f94aaec6a7.mp4?t=1569203209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>卡牌的融合：当你遇见首领后，下次冒险开始时。你将可以通过2次选择卡牌，把两张不同的卡牌融合成一张卡牌。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063140/extras/4c2fe658f7e05d5ed59d43ebcb1102d2.poster.avif?t=1569203209\" width=598 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063140/extras/4c2fe658f7e05d5ed59d43ebcb1102d2.webm?t=1569203209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063140/extras/4c2fe658f7e05d5ed59d43ebcb1102d2.mp4?t=1569203209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>卡牌的强化：尖塔中可能出现事件，不同于卡牌升级的固定强化，事件强化的卡牌能获得一些独特的强化方式。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063140/extras/465964051b8dc2f811676480e65706af.poster.avif?t=1569203209\" width=598 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063140/extras/465964051b8dc2f811676480e65706af.webm?t=1569203209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063140/extras/465964051b8dc2f811676480e65706af.mp4?t=1569203209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>惊心的关卡：一些关卡会有动作过关游戏的感觉，需要你对时机和位置的把握非常准确。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063140/extras/aa7f96da9de9916b38a46c096d856971.poster.avif?t=1569203209\" width=598 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063140/extras/aa7f96da9de9916b38a46c096d856971.webm?t=1569203209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1063140/extras/aa7f96da9de9916b38a46c096d856971.mp4?t=1569203209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>宠物的升级：每个英雄能在开始时选择一个宠物跟随进行冒险，宠物在战斗中随时都能使用，但是战斗完毕后他需要休息一下。<br><br>初始的卡组：每个英雄通过天赋解锁，能在开始时选择3种卡组之一进行冒险。<br><br>随机的牌组：谨慎选择你的卡牌！选择是否将它们加入你的牌组，通过组合和搭配来让牌组发挥力量，打败敌人、挑战登顶。<br><br>变化的尖塔：每次开始爬塔的旅程时，尖塔的构造都会发生变化。是选择高风险高回报，还是谨慎前行？面对不同的敌人。<br><br>强大的宝藏：你将发现各种宝藏，这些宝藏可能会与你的牌组产生强大的化学反应，让你的战力得到飞跃。但也不要过于大意，为了获得遗物，有时你所付出的代价。",
